data.description: Beautiful Summerwood Pulte built 3 bedroom 2 full bath home on the 6th fairway, with premium wedge shaped lot. a multitude of upgrades including  impact windows, tray ceilings, 8ft. The house features crown molding, 5 1/2" baseboard, bullnose countertops throughout, a large walk-in closet, a frameless shower door made of heavy glass, a unique sunroom with custom blinds, a golf cart garage coated with rock solid polycuramine, overhead shelving, Kinetico overdrive whole home water filtration system, and a screened entryway. Take a tour of this luxurious home now.
